    public class JettyHttpConnectionFactory
extends org.eclipse.jetty.server.HttpConnectionFactory
    Extension of the default Jetty HttpConnectionFactory which creates connections with additional properties. Created connections also notify NetworkConnectionTracker when open or closed.
